Author: Vaughn Vernon

Strategic Design Tools
- Bounded Context
- Ubiquitous Language
- Context mapping
- Sub-domains
Tactical Design Tools
- Aggregates - Helps in controlling transactions
- Domain Events - Helps in modelling facts - Occurrence within a domain model

Strategic design is given more significance than tactical design as tactical tools usage is limited based on the technical needs.
DDD is about knowledge acquisition and crunching knowledge.
